{"tid":1669364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家小心D南山邨個白卡婆","createTime":"2019-10-22T13:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T08:15:48.000Z","uid":248934,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"110279f03326e76118bbb5613e418b5603276fb9","tid":1669364,"uid":248934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"南山邨一直有個白卡婆用遮去打下D欄杆，有時會打途人，今日打打下用鎅刀想襲擊中學生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJQn5o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJQn5o.png&h=25110b9c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n特徵: 穿紫色風褸同埋成日用遮去打欄杆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ac44sk6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAc44sk6.gif&h=5c95db7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n向學生吐口水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQbiwVH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQbiwVH.gif&h=caae8e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用遮打人  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇幾耐就攞鎅刀想攻擊中學生，不過冇錄低個段<br />\n之後我問翻，個同學冇受傷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ydHYFJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ydHYFJ.png&h=515d635f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而個白卡婆即日俾人拉咗<br />\n不過應該會因為精神有問題好快放翻出嚟<br />\n南山邨嘅巴打絲打要小心D"},{"pid":"97ab384889a8010fd31a3fdd6e46385eb1ec0735","tid":1669364,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:38:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0885ce158b60638b2a54ea30104faa49e9ea664","tid":1669364,"uid":71508,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:40:49.000Z","msg":"公屋特別多<br />\n我鄰居都係<br />\n我都係<br />\n哈哈大笑"},{"pid":"e42fc5fab9b8460bf99fe5b6f50227bf3bf46c5c","tid":1669364,"uid":248934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T13:45:20.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7b7dd7d8ce7da0ae2944e207c01a8c2ea5e570a0","tid":1669364,"uid